front.title: Set For Stun
front.gametext: Use 2 Force to target one opponent's character. Draw destiny. If destiny > character's ability, character immediately returns to opponent's hand. (Also, any cards deployed on character return to owners' hands.)
front.lore: '...bring me the passengers. I want them alive!' Imperial soldiers use blaster stun settings to intimidate or to capture prisoners for questioning and interrogation.

combo: Set for Stun + Scanning Crew Send a Rebel back into the hand then scan it right into the Used Pile.
